{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3",
    "translationId": "lxxe",
    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 3,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 3 in Brenton's English Septuagint."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.1",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:1",
      "text": "Now these were the sons of David that were born to him in Chebron; the first-born Amnon, born of Achinaam the Jezraelitess; the second Damniel, of Abigaia the Carmelitess.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.2",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:2",
      "text": "The third, Abessalom, the son of Mocha the daughter of Tholmai king of Gedsur; the fourth, Adonia the son of Aggith.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.3",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:3",
      "text": "The fifth, Saphatia, the son of Abital; the sixth, Jethraam, born of Agla his wife.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.4",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:4",
      "text": "Six were born to him in Chebron; and he reigned there seven years and six months: and he reigned thirty-three years in Jerusalem.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.5",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:5",
      "text": "And these were born to him in Jerusalem; Samaa, Sobab, Nathan, and Solomon; four of Bersabee the daughter of Amiel:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.6",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:6",
      "text": "and Ebaar, and Elisa, and Eliphaleth,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.7",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:7",
      "text": "and Nagai, and Naphec, and Japhie,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.8",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:8",
      "text": "and Helisama, and Eliada, and Eliphala, nine.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.9",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:9",
      "text": "All these were the sons of David, besides the sons of the concubines, and there was also Themar their sister.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.10",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:10",
      "text": "The sons of Solomon; Roboam, Abia his son, Asa his son, Josaphat his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.11",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:11",
      "text": "Joram his son, Ochozias his son, Joas his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.12",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:12",
      "text": "Amasias his son, Azarias his son, Joathan his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.13",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:13",
      "text": "Achaz his son, Ezekias his son, Manasses his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.14",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:14",
      "text": "Amon his son, Josia his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.15",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:15",
      "text": "And the sons of Josia; the first-born Joanan, the second Joakim, the third Sedekias, the fourth Salum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.16",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:16",
      "text": "And the sons of Joakim; Jechonias his son, Sedekias his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.17",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:17",
      "text": "And the sons of Jechonias; Asir, Salathiel his son,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.18",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:18",
      "text": "Melchiram, and Phadaias, and Sanesar, and Jekimia, and Hosamath, and Nabadias.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.19",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:19",
      "text": "And the sons of Phadaias; Zorobabel, and Semei: and the sons of Zorobabel; Mosollam, and Anania, and Salomethi was their sister.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.20",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:20",
      "text": "And Asube, and Ool, and Barachia, and Asadia, and Asobed, five.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.21",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:21",
      "text": "And the sons of Anania, Phalettia, and Jesias his son, Raphal his son, Orna his son, Abdia his son, Sechenias his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.22",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:22",
      "text": "And the son of Sechenias; Samaia: and the sons of Samaia; Chattus, and Joel, and Berri and Noadia, and Saphath, six.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.23",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:23",
      "text": "And the sons of Noadia: Elithenan, and Ezekia, and Ezricam, three.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.3.24",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 3:24",
      "text": "And the sons of Elithenan; Odolia, and Heliasebon, and Phadaia, and Akub, and Joanan, and Dalaaia, and Anan, seven.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
